<div id="review_1732802506" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1732802506" />
    <a title="Katayoon Salehi" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/55576206-katayoon-salehi"><img alt="Katayoon Salehi" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1598856394p2/55576206.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1732802506?book_show_action=true">Aug 19, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Katayoon Salehi" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Katayoon Salehi" href="/user/show/55576206-katayoon-salehi">Katayoon Salehi</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9789648497434" href="/book/show/663477._">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1732802506" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4022879871790121328">Mind blowing book! Mixing up Nietzsche&apos; philosophy and psychology by Irvin Yalom is just brilliant. Also a pretty good fiction. Enjoyed every second of reading this book. </span>
  <span id="freeText4022879871790121328" style="display:none">Mind blowing book! Mixing up Nietzsche' philosophy and psychology by Irvin Yalom is just brilliant. Also a pretty good fiction. Enjoyed every second of reading this book. </span>
